Word - Class in baseClasses
the Word class is one of the two basic classes of the whole project: it is the smallest part of the project, and provides useful tools to manage the words contained in a song.
Word(String, String, String) - Constructor for class baseClasses.Word
 
Writer - Class in tools
the Writer class is used to output the result of computations: it contains three methods, each to write a different kind of .csv file, depending on its characteristics.
Writer() - Constructor for class tools.Writer
